pageContext.claim: “It's one thing to say, you know, you ran a great race. Congratulations. I'm OK with that. But they didn't. They didn't run a good race. They ran a horrible race from the basement. They ran a race where he didn't even run. But what they did is, they cheated. They cheated like nobody's ever cheated before that we know of.”
pageContext.analysis: Of course Biden campaigned, but he did it following coronavirus protocols in an effort to model good behavior. He ended up winning so one cannot say he ran a "horrible race."
